{"tid":762310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"官恩娜瑞士山峯餵人奶","createTime":"2018-07-31T07:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T10:30:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aa66602d83f9915fa6c6510f4b4034c8ceab7fe9","tid":762310,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】歌手官恩娜（Ella）近日與老公Juan-Domingo及一對子女到瑞士度假，一直堅持以母乳餵哺的Ella，更在ig張貼自己在瑞士莫雷松山上餵人奶的照片。<br />\n<br />\nElla在ig張貼自己在高山上餵女兒食母乳的照片，從照片可見，Ella神態自若，亦未有使用遮布。她留言稱，「B&eacute;B&eacute; A having lunch on top of the 2002m Mol&eacute;son mountain .＃sommetdumol&eacute;son ＃2002m B&eacute;B&eacute; 在2002米高的莫雷松山食午餐）」。照片得到大批網民支持，有人更留言稱，希望日後亞洲國家四處也設有育嬰室。<br />\n<br />\nElla一向支持母乳餵哺，她曾於2016年時因在五星級酒店的更衣室餵母乳，而慘遭中年婦投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%98%E6%81%A9%E5%A8%9C%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E5%B1%B1%E5%B3%AF%E9%A4%B5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A5%B6-%E7%8D%B2%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%9B%E6%92%90-034900041.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%25A8%259C%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E9%25A4%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B6-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2592%2590-034900041.html&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwSsq17pxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=17ff1874\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%98%E6%81%A9%E5%A8%9C%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E5%B1%B1%E5%B3%AF%E9%A4%B5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A5%B6-%E7%8D%B2%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%9B%E6%92%90-034900041.html</a>"},{"pid":"969513cf7610e30a684be023cd47609485b96d11","tid":762310,"uid":86673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7f94a2d52e